OL,3,CHistoric 500-year-old pub confirms
OL,4,Creopening date
OL,6,FA Grade-II listed pub in Wiltshire has
OL,7,Fset a date for its grand reopening.
OL,9,FThe Hop Pole Inn, in the village of
OL,10,FLimpley Stoke near Bath, will open its
OL,11,Fdoors to the public on Saturday 25
OL,12,FJanuary - nearly three years after the
OL,13,Fcommunity raised nearly #400,000 to
OL,14,Fbuy the site and stop it from being
OL,15,Fturned into housing.
OL,17,FThe pub shared on social media: "Our
OL,18,Fbeautiful Hop Pole Inn is very to
OL,19,Fclose to opening. The date is set for
OL,20,F25 January."
