OL,6,FOn 19 December the new tenants were
OL,7,Frevealed - Charlie Rawlings and Hannah
OL,8,FRandall. The pub's account on social
OL,9,Fmedia said: "Behind every good pub is
OL,10,Fa great landlord. And we have got not
OL,11,Fone but two!
OL,13,F"The team selected Charlie, an
OL,14,Fexceptional chef, and Hannah, the
OL,15,Ffront of house ray of sunshine, with
OL,16,Fhelp from industry experts and glowing
OL,17,Freferences, to run the pub and help us
OL,18,Fall put the heart back into the
OL,19,Fcommunity.
