OL,6,F"So many of us have been working
OL,7,Fclosely with them already and they are
OL,8,Fwell and truly a vital part of the
OL,9,Fteam. They have been hard at work
OL,10,Fgrafting on the interiors and gardens,
OL,11,Ffinalising marketing and branding
OL,12,Fplans, and selecting staff and
OL,13,Fsuppliers.
OL,15,F"They bring with them a wealth of
OL,16,Fexperience in hospitality and have
OL,17,Fexciting plans to bring to the pub. We
OL,18,Flove them and we know you will too."
