OL,3,CHistoric 500-year-old pub confirms
OL,4,Creopening date
OL,6,FThe good news comes after years of
OL,7,Fdifficulties raising funds to restore
OL,8,Fthe pub - with villagers forced to
OL,9,Fraise an extra #300,000 to save the
OL,10,Fbuilding from deteriorating.
OL,12,FThe Hop Pole Inn dates back to 1580
OL,13,Fand was featured in the award-winning
OL,14,Fmovie 'The Remains of the Day'.
OL,16,FAfter buying the pub, campaigners
OL,17,Farrived to find the building suffering
OL,18,Ffrom dry rot, mould and unsupported
OL,19,Fbeams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
