OL,4,Creopening date
OL,6,FLocals from the Save the Hop Pole
OL,7,Fcampaign then had to set up their own
OL,8,F"scrounging teams," asking villagers
OL,9,Fto donate much-needed materials and
OL,10,Fresources.
OL,12,FJames Sibson from the Save the Hop
OL,13,FPole campaign told ITV West Country in
OL,14,FMarch 2024: "We knew we were buying an
OL,15,Fold building and that would bring some
OL,16,Fchallenges, but we didn't realise how
OL,17,Fold it was and we didn't realise how
OL,18,Fflawed the work had been over the last
OL,19,F150 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
