OL,3,CHistoric 500-year-old pub confirms
OL,4,Creopening date
OL,6,F"You make a hole and you find a
OL,7,Fproblem. You make an opening in the
OL,8,Fwall you find a problem."
OL,10,FVictoria Davies spoke to the villagers
OL,11,Ffighting rising building costs to save
OL,12,Fthe pub in March 2024.
OL,14,FSave the Hop Pole committee member
OL,15,FJessica Lloyd-Smith told ITV West
OL,16,FCountry in November 2023: "Without the
OL,17,Fpub the village is a collection of
OL,18,Fhouses. With a pub in it, it gives it
OL,19,Fback its heart again so that is what
OL,20,Fwe are really hoping to do."
